<refsect1 id="GSSDPResourceGroup.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
A <link linkend="GSSDPResourceGroup"><type>GSSDPResourceGroup</type></link> is a group of SSDP resources whose availability can
be controlled as one. This is useful when one needs to announce a single
service as multiple SSDP resources (UPnP does this for example).</para>
<para>
</para>
</refsect1>

